> 30 January - Student demonstrations in Ankara.
> 17 March - Turkey criticizes Israeli invasion of Lebanon.
> 28 May - Fenerbahce wins the championship.
> 31 May - Meeting between Ecevit and U.S. president Jimmy Carter.
> 1 June - Turkan Soray, star in the film Selvi Boylum Al Yazmalim, wins Best Actress in Tashkent Film Festival.
> 11 July - Bedrettin Comert of Hacettepe University killed.
> 27 September - United States lifts embargo on aid to Turkey.
> 11 December - Ahmet Enunlu wins gold in Mr. Universe bodybuilding competition.